gems-patches

This directory is a repository of patches that are applied against GEMS.
For each patch placed in this directory, please add a description here.

gems-2.1.1-pre-build.diff
This patch is applied prior to building GEMS.  If you use the make-gems.sh 
script, this patch is automatically applied.  It corrects a few errors that
are generated when using gcc 4.

gems-magic-break.diff
This patch adds the magic break capability to GEMS (opal), so that 
MAGIC(0x40000) causes simulation to stop.

gems-ctrl-c.diff
This patch adds the ability of GEMS to catch Ctrl+C to break simulation.
It also enables the magic break capability.

